30
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:41,330
So of course we want some kind of
regression technique for

31
00:01:41,330 --> 00:01:42,760
time to event outcomes.

32
00:01:42,760 --> 00:01:44,350
And that's where the Cox Regression comes
in.

33
00:01:44,350 --> 00:01:48,950
It's the multivariate regression technique
