all the things we've talked about.

35
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:55,640
You can have multiple predictors to
improve prediction in the model.

36
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:57,730
You can adjust for confounding, you can
test for

37
00:01:57,730 --> 00:01:59,480
interaction, all those kinds of things.

38
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:04,390
So, Cox Regression is

39
