things is that.

46
00:02:25,210 --> 00:02:28,340
These outcomes take into account
censoring,

47
00:02:28,340 --> 00:02:32,720
we're following people over time and we're
able to say when people drop out of

48
00:02:32,720 --> 00:02:36,270
