00:05:05,780 --> 00:05:07,250
So it's not statistically significant.

96
00:05:07,250 --> 00:05:10,379
It's not a big, of a big magnitude either.

97
00:05:10,379 --> 00:05:13,740
But that's the basic interpretation and

98
00:05:13,740 --> 00:05:16,622
that hazard ratio came out of a Cox
